title: Chicoreus dovi
content:
Chicoreus (Triplex) dovi Houart, 1984

Chicoreus dovi is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Muricidae, the murex snails or rock snails.[1]

This marine species occurs off Kenya.
